c0ae6f1a-1334-4493-8009-c5d2f7ed69d0.title: Note
c0ae6f1a-1334-4493-8009-c5d2f7ed69d0.text: in case players try to skip steps..

f106e14a-5635-4a66-a132-9f08de5d8ad3.title: Bravek
f106e14a-5635-4a66-a132-9f08de5d8ad3.text: My head hurts! I'll speak to you another day...

353f5afd-e69c-4631-b82d-35f719d546ad.title: Bravek
353f5afd-e69c-4631-b82d-35f719d546ad.text:
I can't possibly speak to you with my head spinning like
this... I went a bit heavy on the drink again last night.
Curse my herbalist, she made the best hang over cures.
Darn inconvenient of her catching the plague.

options.text: You shouldn't drink so much then!
Do you know what's in the cure?

359047c9-800c-4129-9e53-27bd9c38ec10.title: <player>
359047c9-800c-4129-9e53-27bd9c38ec10.text: You shouldn't drink so much then!

de1b4e1f-dcdb-43a8-9e6f-824d90ea5087.title: Bravek
de1b4e1f-dcdb-43a8-9e6f-824d90ea5087.text:
Well positions of responsibility are hard, I need
something to take my mind off things... Especially with
the problems this place has.

options.text: Do you know what's in the cure?
I don't think drink is the solution.

5820d0ec-999f-45b1-a4ba-0667bbdf3d12.title: <player>
5820d0ec-999f-45b1-a4ba-0667bbdf3d12.text: I don't think drink is the solution.

e9b1a5db-a23c-462a-ba2e-2f0259a5870a.title: Bravek
e9b1a5db-a23c-462a-ba2e-2f0259a5870a.text:
I don't feel well enough to have a philosophical discussion
about it right now. My head hurts.

options.text: Do you know what's in the cure?

e72a5b28-1534-40ac-bde3-f29b131fd74e.title: <player>
e72a5b28-1534-40ac-bde3-f29b131fd74e.text: Do you know what's in the cure?

75cb7771-916b-40a8-9cf2-6e00d1c91d33.title: Bravek
75cb7771-916b-40a8-9cf2-6e00d1c91d33.text:
Hmmm let me think... Ouch! Thinking isn't clever. Ah
here, she did scribble it down for me.

96697240-ea7f-4473-b84d-3aefce16ea52.text: Bravek hands you a tatty piece of paper.

99a1c61a-c2f8-49db-9492-27f020644eca.title: Note
99a1c61a-c2f8-49db-9492-27f020644eca.text:
a scruffy note
'It seems to say "hongorer lure"...'

138941ad-c257-484a-bb3e-ebbf01f0c6de.title: Bravek
138941ad-c257-484a-bb3e-ebbf01f0c6de.text:
Uurgh! My head still hurts too much to think straight.
Oh for one of Trudi's hangover cures!

54d486d5-9bd5-4571-be65-d72df25dc6b9.title: Bravek
54d486d5-9bd5-4571-be65-d72df25dc6b9.text:
Uurgh! My head still hurts too much to think straight.
Oh for one of Trudi's hangover cures!

94c9fe48-e8b6-4e99-a82c-c28b8ac6397c.title: Note
94c9fe48-e8b6-4e99-a82c-c28b8ac6397c.text: Do you have the Hangover Cure?

3b14d345-b0b2-48f9-8fbe-3685a5292a5e.text:
You give Bravek the hangover cure. Bravek gulps down
the foul-looking liquid.

47c919f8-5e84-4b4b-949a-b11d30bc34c0.title: Bravek
47c919f8-5e84-4b4b-949a-b11d30bc34c0.text:
Ooh that's much better! Thanks, that's the clearest my
head has felt in a month. Ah now, what was it you
wanted me to do for you?

333890a4-d663-4c80-988f-4619137ba0be.title: <player>
333890a4-d663-4c80-988f-4619137ba0be.text:
I need to rescue a kidnap victim called Elena. She's
being held in a plague house, I need permission to
enter.

f0faa547-039b-49b0-a560-36bdc5fa5bea.title: Bravek
f0faa547-039b-49b0-a560-36bdc5fa5bea.text: Well the mourners deal with that sort of thing...

options.text: Okay, I'll go speak to them.
Is that all anyone says around here?

1b25e0cf-572e-4e67-a6aa-c01230e5eecf.title: <player>
1b25e0cf-572e-4e67-a6aa-c01230e5eecf.text: Okay, I'll go speak to them.

034bc4e6-1940-4b77-a012-1f9967e8e952.title: Bravek
034bc4e6-1940-4b77-a012-1f9967e8e952.text: Thanks again for the hangover cure.

928f8f9d-7d0d-48eb-b99a-9a86e84e12e8.title: Bravek
928f8f9d-7d0d-48eb-b99a-9a86e84e12e8.text: Ah now what was it you wanted me to do for you?

39f0dd33-2230-4601-a49b-981979a9eef0.title: <player>
39f0dd33-2230-4601-a49b-981979a9eef0.text:
I need to rescue Elena. She's now a kidnap victim!
She's being held in a plague house, I need permission to
enter.

0b36bb1a-b3f2-4877-8ba7-b7bd0901bc18.title: <player>
0b36bb1a-b3f2-4877-8ba7-b7bd0901bc18.text: Is that all anyone says around here?

ac258f2c-cbc0-4e6c-8f0e-2382b12fdbd9.title: Bravek
ac258f2c-cbc0-4e6c-8f0e-2382b12fdbd9.text: Well, they know best about plague issues.

options.text: Don't you want to take an interest in it at all?

827be5af-af08-4c6c-b6f6-7b30a3404c1b.title: <player>
827be5af-af08-4c6c-b6f6-7b30a3404c1b.text: Don't you want to take an interest in it at all?

01251264-034b-4505-9e3a-4b840022281c.title: Bravek
01251264-034b-4505-9e3a-4b840022281c.text:
Nope, I don't wish to take a deep interest in plagues.
That stuff is too scary for me!

options.text: I see why people say you're a weak leader.
Okay, I'll talk to the mourners.

869867e7-abc9-4fd3-9ce3-ce68040b5371.title: <player>
869867e7-abc9-4fd3-9ce3-ce68040b5371.text: Okay, I'll talk to the mourners.

d55ad266-e553-47dd-820b-7e4f179f9f9c.title: <player>
d55ad266-e553-47dd-820b-7e4f179f9f9c.text: I see why people say you're a weak leader.

13f32e1b-2eea-4af1-ac5f-1c0626c66133.title: Bravek
13f32e1b-2eea-4af1-ac5f-1c0626c66133.text:
Bah, people always criticise their leaders but delegating
is the only way to lead. I delegate all plague issues to
the mourners.

b506c873-5f71-449b-be79-9bfc5b126284.title: <player>
b506c873-5f71-449b-be79-9bfc5b126284.text: This whole city is a plague issue!

1fdc905b-68c3-42df-b107-6ddfb77ca431.title: <player>
1fdc905b-68c3-42df-b107-6ddfb77ca431.text:
They say I'm not properly equipped to go in the house,
though I do have a very effective gas mask.

d19fab6d-0c38-4854-b9ac-14a8087271ba.title: Bravek
d19fab6d-0c38-4854-b9ac-14a8087271ba.text:
Hmmm, well I guess they're not taking the issue of a
kidnapping seriously enough. They do go a bit far
sometimes.

9db5495e-e3eb-4760-b938-36beaa5b151f.title: Bravek
9db5495e-e3eb-4760-b938-36beaa5b151f.text:
I've heard of Elena, she has helped us a lot... Okay, I'll
give you this warrant to enter the house.

ddd61cb6-06db-4196-bf4b-edf75087aff0.title: Note
ddd61cb6-06db-4196-bf4b-edf75087aff0.text:
Warrant
'A search warrant for a house in West Ardougne.'

ccba3c00-8028-441d-916c-9bf0aa392025.title: Bravek
ccba3c00-8028-441d-916c-9bf0aa392025.text: Thanks again for the hangover cure.

d49881ad-87cd-4025-b841-71ebfdb2fec1.title: <player>
d49881ad-87cd-4025-b841-71ebfdb2fec1.text: Not a problem, happy to help out.

1f9862d5-b3b8-4120-84df-3262aac1376f.title: Bravek
1f9862d5-b3b8-4120-84df-3262aac1376f.text:
I'm just having a little drop of whisky, then I'll feel
really good.
